<h2 id="topics-of-the-course">Topics of the course</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Euler Tours</li>
  <li>Hamilton Cycles</li>
  <li>Trees</li>
  <li>Spaces of Graphs</li>
  <li>Planar Graphs</li>
  <li>Networks and Connectivity</li>
  <li>Matching and Independence Number</li>
  <li>Colouring</li>
  <li>Graphs and Groups</li>
  <li>Turan Theorem</li>
  <li>Ramsey Theorem</li>
  <li>Point-Set Theory</li>
  <li>Hypergraphs</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites</h2>
<p>Basic linear algebra, calculus.</p>
